{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}

{% block title %}Veille Technologique — Cloud & DevOps 2023–2025{% endblock %}

{% block meta_description %}Veille technologique Cloud & DevOps 2023–2025 — tendances, statistiques et évolutions majeures par Jérémy Decottignies, BTS SIO.{% endblock %}

{% block stylesheets %}
    {{ parent() }}
    <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Mono:wght@400;500&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">
    <style>
        /* ── Thème sombre spécifique à la veille ── */
        .veille-wrap {
            --vbg:    #05070f;
            --vbg2:   #0b0f1e;
            --vtext:  #e2e8f0;
            --vmuted: #64748b;
            --vacc:   #38bdf8;
            --vacc2:  #818cf8;
            --vacc3:  #34d399;
            --vacc4:  #f59e0b;
            --vacc5:  #f472b6;
            --vborder: rgba(255,255,255,0.07);
            --mono: 'DM Mono', monospace;
            background: var(--vbg);
            color: var(--vtext);
            font-family: var(--font-body, 'DM Sans', sans-serif);
            position: relative;
            overflow-x: hidden;
        }

        /* ── Light mode ── */
        body:not(.dark-mode) .veille-wrap {
            --vbg:     #f5f7fb;
            --vbg2:    #ffffff;
            --vtext:   #111827;
            --vmuted:  #6b7280;
            --vacc:    #2563eb;
            --vacc2:   #7c3aed;
            --vacc3:   #059669;
            --vacc4:   #d97706;
            --vacc5:   #db2777;
            --vborder: rgba(17,24,39,0.10);
        }

        /* ── Light mode grille de fond ── */
        body:not(.dark-mode) .veille-wrap::before {
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(37,99,235,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(37,99,235,0.04) 1px, transparent 1px);
        }

        /* ── Light mode sous-nav ── */
        body:not(.dark-mode) .veille-subnav {
            background: rgba(245,247,251,0.9);
        }

        /* ── Light mode gradients texte ── */
        body:not(.dark-mode) .v-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, #2563eb, #7c3aed);
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        /* Grille de fond */
        .veille-wrap::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 0;
            background-image:
                linear-gradient(rgba(56,189,248,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px),
                linear-gradient(90deg, rgba(56,189,248,0.03) 1px, transparent 1px);
            background-size: 48px 48px;
            pointer-events: none;
            z-index: 0;
        }

        /* Barre de progression */
        #veille-progress {
            position: fixed; top: 0; left: 0; z-index: 200;
            height: 3px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #818cf8);
            width: 0%;
            transition: width .1s;
        }

        /* Ancres internes */
        .veille-subnav {
            position: relative; z-index: 1;
            display: flex; gap: 1.5rem; flex-wrap: wrap;
            justify-content: center;
            padding: 1rem 2rem;
            background: rgba(5,7,15,0.6);
            backdrop-filter: blur(12px);
            border-bottom: 1px solid var(--vborder);
        }

        .veille-subnav a {
            font-size: .8rem;
            color: var(--vmuted);
            text-decoration: none;
            font-family: var(--mono);
            transition: color .2s;
        }

        .veille-subnav a:hover { color: var(--vtext); }

        .veille-badge {
            font-size: .7rem;
            font-family: var(--mono);
            padding: .25rem .7rem;
            border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(56,189,248,.1);
            color: var(--vacc);
            border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,.2);
        }

        /* ── HERO ── */
        .v-hero {
            position: relative; z-index: 1;
            min-height: 80vh;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column;
            align-items: center; justify-content: center;
            text-align: center;
            padding: 5rem 2rem 4rem;
        }

        .v-hero-glow {
            position: absolute;
            width: 600px; height: 600px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            background: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(56,189,248,.08) 0%, transparent 70%);
            top: 50%; left: 50%;
            transform: translate(-50%, -50%);
            pointer-events: none;
        }

        .v-eyebrow {
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .5rem;
            font-family: var(--mono);
            font-size: .75rem;
            color: var(--vacc);
            background: rgba(56,189,248,.08);
            border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,.2);
            border-radius: 999px;
            padding: .3rem .9rem;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            animation: vFadeUp .6s ease both;
        }

        .v-dot {
            width: 6px; height: 6px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--vacc);
            animation: vPulse 2s infinite;
        }

        .v-hero h1 {
            font-family: var(--font-display, 'Syne', sans-serif);
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: clamp(2.5rem, 7vw, 5rem);
            letter-spacing: -.04em;
            line-height: 1.05;
            margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
            color: var(--vtext);
            animation: vFadeUp .6s .1s ease both;
        }

        .v-gradient {
            background: linear-gradient(135deg, var(--vacc), var(--vacc2));
            -webkit-background-clip: text;
            -webkit-text-fill-color: transparent;
            background-clip: text;
        }

        .v-hero p {
            font-size: 1.1rem;
            color: var(--vmuted);
            font-weight: 300;
            max-width: 560px;
            margin: 0 auto 2.5rem;
            animation: vFadeUp .6s .2s ease both;
        }

        .v-stats {
            display: flex; gap: 2rem; justify-content: center; flex-wrap: wrap;
            animation: vFadeUp .6s .3s ease both;
        }

        .v-stat-num {
            font-family: var(--font-display, 'Syne', sans-serif);
            font-size: 1.8rem; font-weight: 800;
            color: var(--vacc); display: block;
        }

        .v-stat-label {
            font-size: .75rem; color: var(--vmuted);
            font-family: var(--mono);
        }

        /* ── SECTIONS ── */
        .v-section {
            position: relative; z-index: 1;
            padding: 5rem 2rem;
            max-width: 1100px;
            margin: 0 auto;
        }

        .v-eyebrow-sm {
            font-family: var(--mono);
            font-size: .75rem; color: var(--vacc);
            letter-spacing: .1em; text-transform: uppercase;
            margin-bottom: .75rem; display: block;
        }

        .v-title {
            font-family: var(--font-display, 'Syne', sans-serif);
            font-weight: 800;
            font-size: clamp(1.8rem, 4vw, 2.8rem);
            letter-spacing: -.03em; line-height: 1.1;
            color: var(--vtext);
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            text-align: center;
        }

        /* ── TIMELINE ── */
        .v-timeline {
            position: relative;
            padding-left: 3rem;
        }

        .v-timeline::before {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            left: 10px; top: 0; bottom: 0; width: 2px;
            background: linear-gradient(to bottom, var(--vacc), var(--vacc2), var(--vacc3));
            opacity: .3;
        }

        .v-tl-item {
            position: relative;
            margin-bottom: 3rem;
            opacity: 0;
            transform: translateX(-20px);
            transition: opacity .6s ease, transform .6s ease;
        }

        .v-tl-item.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }

        .v-tl-dot {
            position: absolute;
            left: -2.75rem; top: .4rem;
            width: 14px; height: 14px;
            border-radius: 50%;
            border: 2px solid var(--vacc);
            background: var(--vbg);
        }

        .v-tl-dot::after {
            content: '';
            position: absolute;
            inset: 3px; border-radius: 50%;
            background: var(--vacc);
        }

        .v-tl-year {
            font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .75rem;
            color: var(--vacc); margin-bottom: .5rem;
            display: inline-flex; align-items: center; gap: .4rem;
            background: rgba(56,189,248,.08);
            padding: .2rem .7rem; border-radius: 999px;
            border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,.15);
        }

        .v-card {
            background: var(--vbg2);
            border: 1px solid var(--vborder);
            border-radius: 1rem; padding: 1.5rem;
            transition: border-color .2s, transform .2s;
        }

        .v-card:hover { border-color: rgba(56,189,248,.3); transform: translateX(4px); }

        .v-card-header {
            display: flex; align-items: flex-start;
            justify-content: space-between; gap: 1rem;
            margin-bottom: 1rem;
        }

        .v-card h3 {
            font-family: var(--font-display, 'Syne', sans-serif);
            font-weight: 700; font-size: 1.1rem; line-height: 1.2;
            color: var(--vtext);
        }

        .v-tag {
            font-size: .65rem; font-family: var(--mono);
            padding: .2rem .6rem; border-radius: 999px;
            white-space: nowrap; flex-shrink: 0;
        }

        .tag-blue   { background: rgba(56,189,248,.1);  color: #38bdf8; border: 1px solid rgba(56,189,248,.2); }
        .tag-purple { background: rgba(129,140,248,.1); color: #818cf8; border: 1px solid rgba(129,140,248,.2); }
        .tag-green  { background: rgba(52,211,153,.1);  color: #34d399; border: 1px solid rgba(52,211,153,.2); }
        .tag-amber  { background: rgba(245,158,11,.1);  color: #f59e0b; border: 1px solid rgba(245,158,11,.2); }
        .tag-pink   { background: rgba(244,114,182,.1); color: #f472b6; border: 1px solid rgba(244,114,182,.2); }

        .v-card p { font-size: .9rem; color: var(--vmuted); line-height: 1.7; margin-bottom: 1rem; }

        .v-tools { display: flex; flex-wrap: wrap; gap: .4rem; }

        .v-pill {
            font-size: .7rem; font-family: var(--mono);
            padding: .2rem .6rem; border-radius: 999px;
            background: rgba(255,255,255,.05);
            color: var(--vmuted); border: 1px solid var(--vborder);
        }

        .v-source {
            margin-top: .75rem; font-size: .72rem;
            color: var(--vmuted); font-family: var(--mono);
            display: flex; align-items: center; gap: .4rem;
        }

        .v-source a { color: var(--vacc); text-decoration: none; opacity: .7; transition: opacity .2s; }
        .v-source a:hover { opacity: 1; }

        /* ── TECH CARDS ── */
        .v-cards-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(300px, 1fr));
            gap: 1.25rem;
        }

        .v-tech-card {
            background: var(--vbg2); border: 1px solid var(--vborder);
            border-radius: 1rem; padding: 1.5rem;
            opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: opacity .5s ease, transform .5s ease, border-color .2s;
        }

        .v-tech-card.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
        .v-tech-card:hover { border-color: rgba(56,189,248,.25); }
        .v-tech-card h3 { font-family: var(--font-display, 'Syne', sans-serif); font-weight: 700; font-size: 1rem; margin-bottom: .5rem; color: var(--vtext); }
        .v-tech-card p { font-size: .875rem; color: var(--vmuted); line-height: 1.65; }

        .v-bar { margin-top: 1rem; height: 3px; border-radius: 999px; background: var(--vborder); overflow: hidden; }
        .v-bar-fill {
            height: 100%; border-radius: 999px;
            background: linear-gradient(90deg, #38bdf8, #818cf8);
            width: 0; transition: width 1.2s ease;
        }
        .v-tech-card.visible .v-bar-fill { width: var(--fill); }
        .v-percent { font-family: var(--mono); font-size: .72rem; color: var(--vacc); margin-top: .4rem; }

        /* ── MARKET ── */
        .v-market-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(200px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem; margin-top: 3rem;
        }

        .v-mstat {
            background: var(--vbg2); border: 1px solid var(--vborder);
            border-radius: 1rem; padding: 1.5rem; text-align: center;
            opacity: 0; transform: translateY(16px);
            transition: opacity .5s ease, transform .5s ease;
        }

        .v-mstat.visible { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
        .v-mstat-num { font-family: var(--font-display, 'Syne', sans-serif); font-weight: 800; font-size: 2rem; display: block; margin-bottom: .25rem; }
        .v-mstat-label { font-size: .8rem; color: var(--vmuted); font-family: var(--mono); }

        /* ── SOURCES ── */
        .v-sources-grid {
            display: grid;
            grid-template-columns: repeat(auto-fit, minmax(260px, 1fr));
            gap: 1rem; margin-top: 2rem;
        }

        .v-src-card {
            background: var(--vbg2); border: 1px solid var(--vborder);
            border-radius: .75rem; padding: 1.25rem;
            display: flex; flex-direction: column; gap: .5rem;
            transition: border-color .2s;
        }

        .v-src-card:hover { border-color: rgba(56,189,248,.2); }
        .v-src-title { font-size: .875rem; font-weight: 500; color: var(--vtext); }
        .v-src-url { font-size: .72rem; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--vacc); opacity: .7; text-decoration: none; word-break: break-all; }
        .v-src-url:hover { opacity: 1; }
        .v-src-type { font-size: .65rem; font-family: var(--mono); color: var(--vmuted); }

        /* ── ANIMATIONS ── */
        @keyframes vFadeUp {
            from { opacity: 0; transform: translateY(20px); }
            to   { opacity: 1; transform: none; }
        }

        @keyframes vPulse {
            0%, 100% { opacity: 1; transform: scale(1); }
            50%       { opacity: .4; transform: scale(1.4); }
        }
    </style>
{% endblock %}

{% block body %}
    <div class="veille-wrap">

        <div id="veille-progress"></div>

        {# Sous-navigation interne #}
        <div class="veille-subnav">
            <a href="#timeline">Timeline</a>
            <a href="#tendances">Tendances</a>
            <a href="#marche">Marché</a>
            <a href="#sources">Sources</a>
            <span class="veille-badge">2023 — 2025</span>
        </div>

        {# ── HERO ── #}
        <section class="v-hero">
            <div class="v-hero-glow"></div>

            <div class="v-eyebrow">
                <span class="v-dot"></span>
                Veille Technologique — BTS SIO
            </div>

            <h1 class="v-hero">
                Cloud &amp;<br>
                <span class="v-gradient">DevOps</span>
            </h1>

            <p>
                Trois ans d'évolutions majeures dans l'écosystème Cloud &amp; DevOps —
                de la montée de Kubernetes à l'IA générative dans les pipelines CI/CD.
            </p>

            <div class="v-stats">
                <div><span class="v-stat-num">$25.5B</span><span class="v-stat-label">marché DevOps 2028</span></div>
                <div><span class="v-stat-num">+19.7%</span><span class="v-stat-label">croissance annuelle</span></div>
                <div><span class="v-stat-num">99%</span><span class="v-stat-label">orga. satisfaites</span></div>
                <div><span class="v-stat-num">80%</span><span class="v-stat-label">adopteront DevOps d'ici 2027</span></div>
            </div>
        </section>

        {# ── TIMELINE ── #}
        <section class="v-section" id="timeline">
            <div style="text-align:center; margin-bottom:4rem;">
                <span class="v-eyebrow-sm">// chronologie</span>
                <h2 class="v-title">Trois ans d'évolutions</h2>
            </div>

            <div class="v-timeline">

                <div class="v-tl-item">
                    <div class="v-tl-dot"></div>
                    <div class="v-tl-year">2023</div>
                    <div class="v-card">
                        <div class="v-card-header">
                            <h3>Kubernetes s'impose comme l'OS du cloud</h3>
                            <span class="v-tag tag-blue">Conteneurisation</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Kubernetes devient la plateforme de référence pour déplacer des charges de travail vers le cloud. Le nombre de clusters K8s augmente cinq fois plus vite que les clusters on-premise. La sécurité, les bases de données et le CI/CD sont les domaines en plus forte croissance sur K8s.</p>
                        <div class="v-tools">
                            <span class="v-pill">Kubernetes</span><span class="v-pill">Docker</span><span class="v-pill">Helm</span><span class="v-pill">ArgoCD</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="v-source">📎 <a href="https://geekflare.com/fr/devops-latest-trends/" target="_blank">geekflare.com — DevOps Trends 2025</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="v-tl-item">
                    <div class="v-tl-dot"></div>
                    <div class="v-tl-year">2023</div>
                    <div class="v-card">
                        <div class="v-card-header">
                            <h3>FinOps : la gestion des coûts cloud mature</h3>
                            <span class="v-tag tag-amber">FinOps</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Le FinOps passe dans la catégorie "early majority". Google devient FinOps Certified Service Provider, Microsoft rejoint la FinOps Foundation. L'optimisation des coûts cloud devient une priorité face au contexte économique tendu.</p>
                        <div class="v-tools">
                            <span class="v-pill">AWS Cost Explorer</span><span class="v-pill">GCP Billing</span><span class="v-pill">CloudHealth</span><span class="v-pill">Infracost</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="v-source">📎 <a href="https://www.infoq.com/articles/cloud-devops-trends-2023/" target="_blank">InfoQ — Cloud & DevOps Trends 2023</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="v-tl-item">
                    <div class="v-tl-dot"></div>
                    <div class="v-tl-year">2023</div>
                    <div class="v-card">
                        <div class="v-card-header">
                            <h3>Infrastructure as Code (IaC) généralisée</h3>
                            <span class="v-tag tag-green">Automatisation</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>L'IaC s'impose comme standard pour provisionner les infrastructures via des fichiers de configuration. Ansible, Terraform et CloudFormation dominent. Le paradigme GitOps émerge : toute modification d'infrastructure passe par un commit Git.</p>
                        <div class="v-tools">
                            <span class="v-pill">Terraform</span><span class="v-pill">Ansible</span><span class="v-pill">CloudFormation</span><span class="v-pill">Pulumi</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="v-source">📎 <a href="https://www.syloe.com/devops-et-cloud-tendances-et-logiciels-en-2023/" target="_blank">Syloe — DevOps & Cloud 2023</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="v-tl-item">
                    <div class="v-tl-dot" style="border-color:#818cf8"></div>
                    <div class="v-tl-year" style="background:rgba(129,140,248,.08);color:#818cf8;border-color:rgba(129,140,248,.2);">2024</div>
                    <div class="v-card">
                        <div class="v-card-header">
                            <h3>DevSecOps : la sécurité intégrée au pipeline</h3>
                            <span class="v-tag tag-purple">Sécurité</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>DevOps publie du code 60% plus rapidement, mais la vitesse introduit des vulnérabilités. DevSecOps intègre la sécurité à chaque phase du pipeline CI/CD. L'approche Zero Trust Networking monte en puissance avec AWS Verified Access lancé en mai 2023.</p>
                        <div class="v-tools">
                            <span class="v-pill">Snyk</span><span class="v-pill">SonarQube</span><span class="v-pill">AWS Verified Access</span><span class="v-pill">Trivy</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="v-source">📎 <a href="https://www.gologic.ca/devops-en-bref-retour-sur-2024-et-les-tendances-pour-2025/" target="_blank">Gologic — DevOps 2024 & 2025</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="v-tl-item">
                    <div class="v-tl-dot" style="border-color:#818cf8"></div>
                    <div class="v-tl-year" style="background:rgba(129,140,248,.08);color:#818cf8;border-color:rgba(129,140,248,.2);">2024</div>
                    <div class="v-card">
                        <div class="v-card-header">
                            <h3>Platform Engineering : l'expérience développeur au centre</h3>
                            <span class="v-tag tag-purple">Platform Eng.</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Les Internal Developer Platforms (IDP) permettent aux équipes de déployer en self-service. La communauté Slack de Platform Engineering passe de 1 000 à 8 000 praticiens. Gartner prédit que 80% des orgs intégreront des plateformes DevOps d'ici 2027.</p>
                        <div class="v-tools">
                            <span class="v-pill">Backstage</span><span class="v-pill">Port</span><span class="v-pill">Humanitec</span><span class="v-pill">Cortex</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="v-source">📎 <a href="https://www.infoq.com/articles/cloud-devops-trends-2025/" target="_blank">InfoQ — Cloud & DevOps Trends Report 2025</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="v-tl-item">
                    <div class="v-tl-dot" style="border-color:#818cf8"></div>
                    <div class="v-tl-year" style="background:rgba(129,140,248,.08);color:#818cf8;border-color:rgba(129,140,248,.2);">2024</div>
                    <div class="v-card">
                        <div class="v-card-header">
                            <h3>Serverless : 9 milliards $ et +25% de croissance annuelle</h3>
                            <span class="v-tag tag-pink">Serverless</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Le marché du serverless dépasse les 9 milliards de dollars avec un CAGR de 25% prévu jusqu'en 2032. AWS Lambda, Google Cloud Functions et Azure Functions dominent. Le cloud passe d'une révolution à une évolution.</p>
                        <div class="v-tools">
                            <span class="v-pill">AWS Lambda</span><span class="v-pill">Cloud Functions</span><span class="v-pill">Azure Functions</span><span class="v-pill">Vercel</span>
                        </div>
                        <div class="v-source">📎 <a href="https://geekflare.com/fr/devops-latest-trends/" target="_blank">Geekflare — Serverless Market Stats</a></div>
                    </div>
                </div>

                <div class="v-tl-item">
                    <div class="v-tl-dot" style="border-color:#34d399"></div>
                    <div class="v-tl-year" style="background:rgba(52,211,153,.08);color:#34d399;border-color:rgba(52,211,153,.2);">2025</div>
                    <div class="v-card">
                        <div class="v-card-header">
                            <h3>AI Agents pour le cloud engineering</h3>
                            <span class="v-tag tag-green">IA & DevOps</span>
                        </div>
                        <p>Les agents IA entrent dans les pipelines DevOps. Le protocole MCP d'Anthropic (nov. 2024) standardise l'intégration des LLMs avec les outils cloud. OpenAI, Microsoft et Google annoncent leur support MCP. L'adoption enterprise est freinée par la compliance.</p>
                        <div class="v-tools">
